OL,6,FA man from has been jailed following a
OL,7,Fhit and run crash which killed a
OL,8,Fpensioner in New Milton.
OL,10,FLewis Griffiths-Bungard, 26, of Vaggs
OL,11,FLane, Hordle, was driving a Citroen C1
OL,12,Fwhen he hit Jill Stevens as she was
OL,13,Fcrossing Old Milton Road in March 2022.
OL,15,FThe 75-year-old died from her injuries.
OL,17,FGriffiths-Bungard did not stay at the
OL,18,Fscene and drove off.
